    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|praticos</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798057647570.032628696870291685\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 35px; top: 68px; width: 596px; height: 62px; z-index: 11;\"><p>Associa diretório local a diretório remoto</p><ul><li><p><strong><em>git remote add origin </em></strong><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://github.com/usuario/projeto.git\"><strong><em>https://github.com/usuario/projeto.git</em></strong></a></p></li></ul><p></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798058573210.6760893422862003\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 35px; top: 157px; width: 668px; height: 75px; z-index: 24;\"><h3>git remote -v  <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">( mostra diretórios remotos )</span></h3><p>origin  <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://github.com/radameslangner/HTML-TO-VIEW.git\">https://github.com/radameslangner/HTML-TO-VIEW.git</a> (fetch)</p><p>origin  <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://github.com/radameslangner/HTML-TO-VIEW.git\">https://github.com/radameslangner/HTML-TO-VIEW.git</a> (push)Terceiro item</p><p></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798059826270.6520245078061561\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 35px; top: 261px; width: 643px; height: 72px; z-index: 16;\"><p>!!! Cuidado Atualizar o nome da branch principal de master para main</p><p></p><p><strong><em>git branch -M main</em></strong></p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798061410870.687889930030678\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 37px; top: 361px; width: 592px; height: 30px; z-index: 22;\"><p><strong><em>git branch -m master main     -    </em></strong>Muda branch de master para main.</p></div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798064695770.9751676657750267\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 37px; top: 419px; width: 658px; height: 47px; z-index: 35;\"><p><strong><em>git branch --show-current</em></strong>     -   Mostra branch atual</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 83, 143);\"><strong>main</strong></span></p></div>"
